text: Avdotyinka () is a rural locality (a village) in Zheludevskoye Rural Settlement of Shilovsky District, Ryazan Oblast, Russia. The population was 549 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == The village is located on Oka–Don Lowland, 10 km south from Shilovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ryazan Oblast
title: Avdotyinka
